creator: Christmas Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Christmas is an intuitive, modern advisor for modern investors. We actively manage your portfolio to beat the stock market.

EVERYTHING AT YOUR FINGERTIPS.
Use this app to create an account (onboard), make deposit/withdrawal, monitor your assets, review your performance, and communicate with us.

INVEST WITH PROVEN PORTFOLIO STRATEGY
Our portfolio strategy is crafted using a leading-edge proprietary strategy proven to beat the market since 2016.

YOUR PRIVATE INVESTMENT MANAGER
Think of us as your private investment manager, who act on your behalf. We aim to grow your assets. As we provide fee-based investment services, when you do well — we do well. Connect with us anytime using our in-app chat system.

WE EAT WHAT WE COOK
We invest our own assets using the same strategy to manage your assets.

LOGIN (EXISTING CLIENTS)
You can login using your email which has been registered with both Christmas Corp and Interactive Brokers.

Christmas Corporation (“Christmas”) is an investment adviser registered with the Securities and Exchange Commission (“SEC”). We manage clients' money in the stock market using separately managed account (SMA) scheme on a discretionary basis, which means we make all investment decisions for you and review your investment account continuously. By using SMA, you own the entire asset, and each stock in the portfolio is owned directly by you. Assets in your account are held under your name at Interactive Brokers, LLC (“IBKR”) as the execution broker, clearing broker, and custodian. IBKR is an SEC-registered broker-dealer and member of FINRA/SIPC.

Investments in securities: Not FDIC Insured - No Bank Guarantee - May Lose Value, and there is always the potential of losing money when you invest in securities. Past performance is no guarantee of future results.
